        <headline>Beach Hazards Statement issued September 4 at 2:46PM CDT until September 5 at 4:00PM CDT by NWS Chicago IL</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...High wave action and dangerous currents at Lake Michigan
beaches expected.

* WHERE...Porter County.

* WHEN...From Friday morning through Friday afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Swimming conditions will be life threatening,
especially for inexperienced swimmers.
</description>
        <instruction>Remain out of the water to avoid dangerous swimming conditions
and do not venture out onto piers, jetties, breakwalls, or other
shoreline structures.</instruction>
